          <p>
            &#x26;nbsp;
          </p>
          -Show them each grade category
        </p>

        <p>
          <em>TA notes:</em> If you have discussion before the first day of lecture, you’ll only do Worksheet 1. Worksheet 1 covers the basics of linear systems without setting up the augmented matrix, and it does introduce some terminology (ex: homogeneous, consistent/inconsistent) that will be defined in lecture in future class meetings.
